{"tid":1852063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓首次出現新型肺炎確診病例　患者來自武漢","createTime":"2020-01-30T09:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T10:14:01.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"66596d7f677100aee6a1cba4c7e2068c4407fcd2","tid":1852063,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:34:49.000Z","msg":"菲律賓首次出現新型冠狀病毒肺炎確診病例，患者來自武漢。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓衛生部長說，來自武漢的38歲女患者，本月21日乘搭飛機經香港抵達馬尼拉，本月25日因輕微咳嗽求診，樣本測試對新型冠狀病毒呈陽性，目前在醫院接受治療。她求診前曾經在宿霧旅遊，當局正追蹤密切接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505679-20200130.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505679-20200130.htm&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=124f43fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505679-20200130.htm&h=fc4ca4ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505679-20200130.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0cf5f0b143a7de70a374e840c5345766431ccb29","tid":1852063,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ba7a195361e4842c9a40fa5a0afa78f167fa89","tid":1852063,"uid":143151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:39:44.000Z","msg":"經香港 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68818554241299c788c21ebcb35918c46811e24","tid":1852063,"uid":35682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"10單有9單都來自武漢<br />\n武漢人感染率奇高<br />\n你話武漢爆左個炸彈我都信"}]}